        <item>
          <title>No. 1 Ohio State tops No. 15 Michigan 27-9, will play No. 2 Indiana for B10 title</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Julian Sayin threw three touchdown passes, including a 35-yarder to Jeremiah Smith on a fourth down in the second quarter, and No. 1 Ohio State beat No. 15 Michigan 27-9 in a dominant performance.]]></description>
